Package hotelproject.controllers.db

Class RoomsDB

java.lang.Object
hotelproject.controllers.db.RoomsDB
public class RoomsDB
extends java.lang.Object
This class contains all the database operations related to rooms. Include add room type, add room, delete room type, delete room, update room type, update room, view room details, find all room types, find all rooms, if room type exist, if room exist, find all booked rooms, and find all room numbers.
